               stealing, on the <rs id="t18160918-104-cd544" type="crimeDate">21st of July</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18160918-104-off543 t18160918-104-cd544"></join>, two live geese, value 5s. a spade, value 1s. and a bag, value 2d.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18160918-104-victim819" type="victimName">
                     Thomas 
